column4: NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "B0F2C9844F596D740070B3B011330C71", "Good, the sewer is back to normal.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "0523AF984799493912EE3CABEF1A48A5", "He\'ll be alright now. I solved the problem.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "09F7613D48FFFCC85ECCC99E32829EFF", "I\'m tired. What happened to you guys?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "A1B6FDF3469466F9302DF4A0D51CF3C7", "He sounds dumber! Maybe he regained his senses.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "9888BC314AAD7991BB3A4FA3D32EF14E", "Are you calling me dumb? How rude! My name is Numemon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "7396E6844BC0F73F10A078802842AD43", "If you\'re not dumb, what are you?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "E2DC01CF4EB21104B03EDF81333E9BE5", "Excuse me, Numemon. Do you know who saved your life?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "C04808C3443E8721AF9C0AA9517B85A5", "Huh? Do you want me to save your life? OK.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "647A0E854AC4C63CC334C8BA9328C0B7", "Ugghh. He doesn\'t get it at all! Well, no matter.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6D9BF84544032CAA6F3560B9631C5CB7]", "2292D1414212CA331B43209195B770E2", "Please come to our city. Do you know where it is?")
